  "text": "Based on Tator scores [CITATION_1] , the therapeutic effects of the surgeries were categorized as valid or invalid. Any decline, improvement, or lack of an obvious change in the symptoms or signs of CM I-SM were considered valid. Exacerbation of the original symptoms or signs of the patients was considered invalid.",
